Currently supported network: VLS Testnet LocalDevNet To add new network, you need to: update local .env edit ./deploy-config/{chain_id}.json, add required params. # With verification
forge script script/Deploy.s.sol:Deploy \
--chain-id $CHAIN_ID \
--rpc-url $RPC_URL \
--private-key $PRIVATE_KEY \
--verifier-url $VERIFIER_URL \
--verifier $VERIFIER \
--verify \
--etherscan-api-key $ETHERSCAN_API_KEY \
--broadcast --ffi -vvvv # Without verification
forge script script/Deploy.s.sol:Deploy \
--chain-id $CHAIN_ID \
--rpc-url $RPC_URL \
--private-key $PRIVATE_KEY \
--broadcast --ffi -vvvv # generate easily readable abi to /deployments
forge script script/Deploy.s.sol:Deploy --sig 'sync()' --rpc-url $RPC_URL --broadcast --ffi
